International RnB singer R Kelly was arrested on Friday night over the 10 criminal sexual abuse charges that have been happening over the past 10 years. According to CNN, R Kelly came up with $100 000 bail on Monday. R Kelly has pleaded not guilty for the alleged crimes. His attorney Steve Greenberg told CNN, " I think all the women are lying. Mr. Kelly is strong, he's got a lot of support and he's going to be vindicated on all these charges -one by one if it has to be.". This investigation still continues.